<div class="invoice">
	<h1>View and Download copies of your Travel Invoices</h1>
	<p>View and download exact copies of your invoice in PDF format. Click the "View/Download" link next to the invoice you want to view, print or save to your computer.</p>
	<div id="outError" align="left">
		@Html.Raw(@ViewBag.OutError)
	</div>
	<div id="Results" class="body" align="left">
		@Html.Raw(@ViewBag.Results)
	</div>
	<div id="Adobe" width="500" style="margin-top:20px;color:#585858"
		@if (@ViewBag.Adobe == true)
		{
			<text>style="display:block"</text>
		}
		else if (@ViewBag.Adobe == false)
		{
			<text>style="display:none"</text>
		}        
		>
		<h2>Need Adobe&reg; Reader</h2>
		<p>To view a PDF copy of statement only, you must have Acrobat&reg; Reader&reg; installed on your computer. You can download the free software from the <a href="http://www.pacific.adobe.com/products/acrobat/readstep2.html?c=au" target="_new">Adobe site</a>.</p>
	</div>
	<h2>Order Past Invoices</h2>
	<p>If your Travel Invoice does not appear and you would like a paper copy please contact your Travel Team. Please note: A fee may apply for invoice reprints.</p>
</div>
